725906f-a.text:
150th Street, north from 14th Road, showing Whitestone's business center. A trolley line at one time operated here and the street was known as Eighth Avenue and also as Irving Place.
March 5, 1932
P. L. Sperr

725895f-a.text: 14-16 150th Street, east side, south of 14th Avenue, showing the Whitestone branch of the Queensboro Public Library. 150th Street was previously know as Eighth Avenue. April 13,1927
